Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.94,0:00:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling, Mr. Junkers?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.98,0:00:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Junkers, do you recognize me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.90,0:00:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you see this finger?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.33,0:00:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it? Can you answer me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.04,0:00:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.71,0:00:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mons... comi...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that, Mr. Junkers?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.63,0:00:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The monster... coming...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.34,0:00:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming...? What's coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.14,0:00:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The monster is coming...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster...is coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.15,0:00:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.24,0:02:28.00,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,750)\pos(360,340)}Night of the Execution
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Junkers...\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're able to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.21,0:02:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Of the four murders of middle-aged couples\Nin the past two years,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.42,0:02:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you were spotted near the scene\Nof three of them, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it, Adolph Junkers?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind. We know that\Nyou are a lock picker.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.36,0:02:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Your job is just to open locks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.49,0:03:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Slitting throats\Nin a single stroke...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't something you could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.71,0:03:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,\NThat means there were other perpetrators\Nin addition to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.71,0:03:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that there would have to be\Nat least three people
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to open a strong lock,\N and murder a middle-aged couple without struggle...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost finished\Nmaking a list of men who use knives.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a matter of time\Nbefore we pinpoint your colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you talk, or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.61,0:03:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But that is not what\NI really want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.99,0:03:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why four couples\Nfrom across Germany?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.41,0:03:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And why only kill\Nmiddle-aged ones without children?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Money and items were stolen,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:04:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but the amounts were too small\Nto split three ways to justify murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.59,0:04:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it?\NWant to make a plea bargain?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.56,0:04:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you make a statement,\Nyou can escape prosecution...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Who asked you to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Junkers! That's enough.\NThat's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to ask you to\Nend this questioning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.79,0:04:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No, just a little bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Please leave this room!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an order from\Nhis attending physician!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, all right.\NI'll come again another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But I will place a guard\Nto watch him closely
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,so that he isn't poisoned\Nor so he doesn't disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma, for some reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:05:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,all kinds of trouble\Nseems to happen around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a joke.\NExcuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing things without permission\Nis gonna get me in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Even patients need recreation.\NWe're just going out into the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're worried,\Ndo you want to come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.95,0:05:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a warm and pleasant day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You can talk, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.54,0:05:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,On days like this,\Nit makes you glad you're alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I need days like this,\Nor else it becomes unbearable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I see people in\Nlife and death situations every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why it's easier for doctors to\Nfocus on fame and research.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to be like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to gain a reputation\Nand do my own research...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.36,0:06:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that succeeding in surgery\Nwas a way to fortify my status.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But after performing surgery\Non a little boy, I changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He was the elder of fraternal twins.\NHe'd been shot in the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,After I saved him, I was able to\Nreturn to being a real doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.96,0:06:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The weight of people's lives\Nare all the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A doctor's work\Nis to save those lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You can start over.\NIt's not too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.74,0:07:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.37,0:07:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I are close in age,\Nbut you're like my old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.21,0:07:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like you're my parent...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I suddenly have a big kid, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was little,\NI wanted a mechanical clock...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind where a nutcracker doll\Nwould stroll out on the hour...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.52,0:07:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Every day I would press my face against\Nthe window of that store...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,My first break was in was that store...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:08:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They caught me right away\Nand I didn't get the clock...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.67,0:08:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But, after that,\Nbreak ins became my job...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,At first, it was only because\NI wanted that clock...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.18,0:08:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I only wanted the clock...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell them everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.94,0:08:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell the police everything\Nand start over from scratch...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My associates, all of them...\NThey were all killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Who killed them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The one you called "The monster"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:08:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Make this one yours, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.31,0:09:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I went through a lot of trouble\Nto set this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the daughter of a\Nstate parliament member, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,She is beautiful and intelligent.\NShe's really something...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.32,0:09:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to meet her first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But...I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I should do as you say\Nand settle down...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You should!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,For someone with your prestige\Nto not have a wife... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The kind where a nutcracker doll\Nwould pop out every hour...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.18,0:09:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!\NAbout the clock in the window...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What's going on?!\NIt's already time for your date! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:10:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You can start over.\NIt's not too late.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.67,0:10:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Officer... Policeman on watch...\NYou're there, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.51,0:10:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But can you call Dr. Tenma, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.73,0:10:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's late, but can I visit\None of the rooms?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course, Dr. Tenma.\NWhat is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:10:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I found something good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.11,0:11:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a hold of yourself...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.79,0:11:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Candy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Junkers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.81,0:11:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Junkers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.56,0:11:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the same as the last time...!\NPoisoned by candy!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:11:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My patient's disappeared...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:12:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same thing that happened\Nnine years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Junkers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Junkers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me, Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.31,0:12:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't come, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.03,0:12:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back to the hospital,\NMr. Junkers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything will be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.24,0:12:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't, Doctor. You mustn't come!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.58,0:12:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't see him, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,"Him?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.55,0:13:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the one\Nwho killed my accomplices!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be killed, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.73,0:13:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't, Doctor! You mustn't come!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time, Doctor.\NIt's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine years ago, you saved my life,\Ndidn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine years ago?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you already forgotten\Nabout those twins?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.63,0:13:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.86,0:14:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, those twins...\NYou remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.99,0:14:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!\NDoctor he'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What do you intend to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.57,0:14:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Junkers is my patient!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Execute him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.59,0:14:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, run!\NHe killed my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.51,0:14:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We were hired by him!\NHe always called us on the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.48,0:14:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A large reward was transferred into\Nour account after each job was done...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'd split it between the three of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who committed the murders\Nof those four middle-aged couples
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,was you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The police were watching me,\Nso we became a hindrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.25,0:15:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He's already killed Fritz the Slayer,\Nand Big Boy Boris!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.58,0:15:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Just before he died, Fritz said...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.76,0:15:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"We've been hired by a monster."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.39,0:15:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't think anything of\Nkilling people!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Run! Doctor, you'll be killed!\NRun, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You talk too much, Junkers...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it, Johan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.19,0:15:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Junkers doesn't seem to know\Nwho you are, but I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I was your attending physician!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.91,0:15:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You are Johan Liebert, the elder of twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the son of Michael Liebert,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.54,0:15:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,former advisor of Commerce\Nin East Germany,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,who defected to West Germany\Nin 1986.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If we know this much about you,\Nyou can't possibly escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't add to your crimes, Johan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan...?\NI used that name before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But that is not my real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.77,0:16:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,My past must not be known.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.86,0:16:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Those four couples\Nand the Lieberts, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're different, Doctor...\NYou saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're like my parent, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Parent...me...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.96,0:16:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, if it weren't for you,\NI wouldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.68,0:16:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!\NYou mustn't kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,"Why not?"\NWhat do you think a human life is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.81,0:16:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I saved your life,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I was able to go back to being\Nwhat a doctor should be!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,By saving your life,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.57,0:16:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized that\Nthe weight of each life is equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.53,0:16:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No one has the right to\Ntake another person's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.37,0:17:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I've lived for many years as a doctor\Nwith that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.67,0:17:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, after that incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.09,0:17:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you soon became\Nthe Chief of Surgery...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.18,0:17:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad that you were selected\Nas the Chief of Surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it you want to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.27,0:17:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here now because the Director, Chief of Surgery\Nand the Chief died, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's really good...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.00,0:17:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be... You did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.37,0:17:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, you said it yourself...\NThis is what you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.80,0:17:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,When I became conscious,\Nthat's what you said
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:17:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That you hated them so much\Nyou could kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am not wrong!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.93,0:18:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That bastard... That bastard...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.19,0:18:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's better off dead.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.73,0:18:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...off dead...off dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I did just as you wished, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.16,0:18:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor...I'm scared, Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor... Save me, Doctor...\NI don't want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.74,0:19:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I was supposed to die back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.32,0:19:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You brought me back to life, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, this rain is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.91,0:19:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate the rain. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It washes away\Nall the evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... based\Non what you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.18,0:20:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,In 1986, right after the Lieberts\Ndefected from East Germany
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,with their twin children,\Nthe Liebert family was shot
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.49,0:20:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and the parents died.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.24,0:20:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The elder of the twins\Nwas shot in the head
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.24,0:20:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You operated on the boy\Nand saved his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But, surprisingly, the boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.21,0:20:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,killed the director, chief of surgery\Nand head of neurosurgery
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,with poisoned candy and ran away...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And last night, he appeared\Nafter nine years
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.35,0:20:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,killing a state police officer.\N Again with poisoned candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.27,0:20:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And shot Adolph Junkers\Nright in front of your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.98,0:20:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He is the one who hired\NJunkers and two others
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:21:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,to kill the four middle-aged couples.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.11,0:21:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is Johan Liebert.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's all of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.79,0:21:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.\N-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.67,0:21:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You can let him go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.01,0:21:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you ever think that someone with\NDr. Tenma's credentials
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.72,0:21:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,would ever commit such a crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.14,0:21:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He has an alibi for the time\Nthe policeman was killed,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.35,0:21:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and there was no gunpowder residue\Non his hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.90,0:21:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, the clue to solving\Nthe murders
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,of those middle-aged couples\Nis gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.36,0:21:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,For the time being, shall we\Ngo after this Johan Liebert?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.12,0:21:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Lunge...
